import React from 'react' function MovieRec(props) { //userGenreList = props.userGenreList const userGenreList = ['romantic', 'adventure', 'sci-fi', 'suspense', 'anime'] const userMovieList = ['tt4566758'] let counter = 0 let omdbData let textToBeDisplayed = userGenreList[Math.round(Math.random() * userGenreList.length)] fetch("http://www.omdbapi.com/?apikey=[906b7c64]&i=" + userMovieList[counter].toString()) .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { omdbData = data }) return ( <>
{/*

{textToBeDisplayed}

*/}

{omdbData.Title}

Genre: {omdbData.Genre}

Director: {omdbData.Director}

{omdbData.Plot}

) } export default MovieRec
